Teaching Sophie the importance of being grateful to essential services so that we may still have our groceries delivered :) Asked her what can she do? She said “Draw a Thank You note! and paste it on our door so that our @redmartcom delivery personnel can see” 😀⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣
#pg #thanksfordelivering #becomingsupermom
That’s so awesome of you guys!
This is lovely!!! Gratitude is something we can't learn from school! ❤️
So nice that kids know who are the heroes in this tough time
Her drawings similar to my girl’s! Very rainbow-ish ❤️
Aww... this is truly teaching the right values in life! 🙌🏻💕Way to go dearie
Sweet initiative for our heros this period
Gratitude is something that needs to be taught
That's a very nice gesture n teaching... ❤️ U r awesome mummy 😘
Her block letterings are sooo pretty!
